title: We Spin the Wheel for Someone to Do Something Embarrassing!!! + Runaway June Stops by to Perform + Easy Trivia Returns!
itunes:title: We Spin the Wheel for Someone to Do Something Embarrassing!!! + Runaway June Stops by to Perform + Easy Trivia Returns!
description:
We spin the wheel and the loser has to watch the new Paw Patrol movie over the weekend and give a review on Monday. Runaway June stops by to talk about their new EP, everyone getting married and perform some songs for us! We start a new round of Easy Trivia as we look for the new champion to wear the tiara.

Learn more about your ad-choices at https://www.iheartpodcastnetwork.com

See omnystudio.com/listener for privacy information.
